```

YAML override precedence:

```text
HF config defaults < adapter inferred values < YAML overrides
```

This is important because newer model configs may rename fields or introduce architecture components before the estimator knows them automatically.

## Component Model

Each component returns independent cost pieces:

```python
ComponentCost(
    bandwidth_units: float,
    flops_units: float,
    cache_units: float,
    attention_score_units: float,
)
```

Estimator sums selected components:

```text
total_flops = sum(component.flops_units + component.attention_score_units)
total_bytes = sum(component.bandwidth_units + component.cache_units) * precision_bytes
```

Then:

```text
S-MFU = total_flops * 2 * throughput / (num_gpus * peak_flops_tf / 2)
S-MBU = total_bytes / latency / (num_gpus * peak_bandwidth_tb)
```

Keep fractions internally. Reports can multiply by 100.

## Required Components

Implement these as independent modules/classes:

```text
AttentionComponent
CacheComponent
DenseFFNComponent
MoEComponent
RouterComponent
LinearAttentionComponent
SparseAttentionComponent
HybridAttentionComponent
```

### Cache Components

```text
KV cache:
  per_token = 2 * layers * head_dim * kv_heads

DeepSeek MLA latent KV:
  per_token = layers * (kv_lora_rank + qk_rope_head_dim)

Sparse KV:
  per_token = KV cache per token * sparse_factor

Linear/recurrent state:
  per_token = layers * recurrent_state_size
```

### Attention Components

MHA/GQA projection size:

```text
hidden * (attention_heads * head_dim + 2 * kv_heads * head_dim)
+ attention_heads * head_dim * hidden
```

DeepSeek MLA projection size:

```text
q_head_dim = qk_rope_head_dim + qk_nope_head_dim

base = hidden * (kv_lora_rank + qk_rope_head_dim)
     + kv_lora_rank * attention_heads * (q_head_dim - qk_rope_head_dim + v_head_dim)
     + v_head_dim * attention_heads * hidden

if q_lora_rank exists:
  q_size = hidden * q_lora_rank + q_lora_rank * attention_heads * q_head_dim
else:
  q_size = hidden * attention_heads * q_head_dim

attention_size_per_token = base + q_size
```

Sparse attention:

```text
attention_score_cost = dense_attention_score_cost * sparse_factor
```

Linear attention:

```text
attention_score_cost = recurrent_state_update_cost
cache_cost = recurrent_state_read_write_cost
```

The exact linear-attention state formula should be supplied by YAML override until a specific model family is validated.

### MoE Components

```text
expert_size = expert_intermediate_size * 3 * hidden / 1e12
shared_expert_size = shared_expert_intermediate_size * 3 * hidden / 1e12
                     if explicit shared size exists
                     else shared_experts * expert_size

MoE bandwidth = moe_layers * (expert_activation * expert_size + shared_expert_size)
MoE FLOPs     = moe_layers * (expert_size + shared_expert_size)
```

Router cost is separate:

```text
router_flops = moe_layers * tokens * hidden * routed_experts
```

Include it as a component so it can be disabled or scaled if top-k/router implementation differs.

## Adapter Registry

Adapters choose descriptors and component sets. They should not directly compute S-MFU/S-MBU.

Required adapters:

```text
DenseTransformerAdapter
QwenMoEAdapter
QwenHybridAdapter
DeepSeekMLAAdapter
DeepSeekSparseAdapter
LinearAttentionAdapter
```

Selection rules:

```text
DeepSeekSparseAdapter:
  DeepSeek model/config + sparse/dsa attention fields or override

DeepSeekMLAAdapter:
  kv_lora_rank + qk_rope_head_dim

QwenHybridAdapter:
  Qwen Next / hybrid / linear/sparse attention config or override

QwenMoEAdapter:
  Qwen config + moe_intermediate_size

LinearAttentionAdapter:
  attention.type = linear override or known linear-attention config

DenseTransformerAdapter:
  fallback
```

Component mix examples:

```text
Qwen3 MoE:
  GQA/MHA Attention + KV Cache + DenseFFN + MoE + Router

Qwen3-Next / hybrid:
  HybridAttention + chosen cache component + DenseFFN + MoE + Router

DeepSeek V3/V4 MLA:
  MLA Attention + LatentKV Cache + DenseFFN + MoE + Router

DeepSeek sparse attention:
  Sparse/DSA Attention + SparseKV or LatentKV Cache + DenseFFN + MoE + Router

Linear attention model:
  LinearAttention + RecurrentState Cache + DenseFFN/MoE as config dictates
```

